reviewText: very good  cops shows and done nicely worth owning
A Must for anyone who stills loves and remembers the "oldies" but "goodies" from the '70s and '80s
Good small taste of these shows first few episodes.  They offer an assortment of what was popular in the classic television category.
It was fun to look at these raw cop shows from the 70's.  Somehow, they are still better then what's on TV now!!
